{"tid":857332,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊隻散光月con好用？","createTime":"2018-10-11T04:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T04:31:35.000Z","uid":36869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4c763f6c803d8312154f2a137e949f44ea5427","tid":857332,"uid":36869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"前排買過Air Optix for Astigmatism<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/122532_921d45af4ef2523d2bb07532891b2357.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F122532_921d45af4ef2523d2bb07532891b2357.jpeg&h=3d2f8ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n$200@3隻<br />\n本身諗住佢貴會潤啲 但普通返工吹下冷氣都係要滴眼藥水先唔乾 所以想轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCooper Vision 就不了 以前帶過佢透明散光 普通color con 都係成日移位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見買開間店仲有隻Colebo 38 Toric Monthly<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/122900_568d10fdfa2ca058064dce0de8f09bf9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F122900_568d10fdfa2ca058064dce0de8f09bf9.jpeg&h=236e7ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但搵唔到網上有啲咩評價<br />\n<br />\n之後另一隻Acuvue Oasys for Astigmatism <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/123011_b5e28ce08b7aab5e4bdf81095e9f56e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F123011_b5e28ce08b7aab5e4bdf81095e9f56e4.jpg&h=9319e17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但又成日聽日論acuvue 又貴又唔好用<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打用過呢兩隻 或者有其他推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"}]}